description: Demo simulation: 35s cycle exercising all pedals (A,B,C), all levers (LKL,LKR,LKV,RKL,RKR), volume, bar slides, and string picks.

packet_schema.sens: hall-effect sensor readings [f0, f5, f10, f15], range 0.000–1.000
packet_schema.ped: pedal engagement [A, B, C], range 0.000–1.000 (>0.5 = engaged)
packet_schema.lev: lever engagement [LKL, LKR, LKV, RKL, RKR], range 0.000–1.000 (>0.5 = engaged)
packet_schema.picks: per-string activation [str1..str10], boolean (from hex pickup RMS threshold)
